Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To rescue his brother Ace who \Nhas been captured by the navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy stowed away on a navy ship with \Nthe Pirate Empress Boa Hancock's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you \Nheard about Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked a fight with the World \NGovernment at Water Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroyed the Judgement \NIsland - Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I told Luffy \Nabout his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was surprised to \Nknow about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Luffy and \NI unfortunately
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have the blood of the world's most \Ninfamous criminal in our veins anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way for \Nus to become marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took over the name "Portgaz" from \Nmy mother to whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never wanted to have my \Ngood-for-nothing father's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have any memory of \Nhim and I don't owe anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yeah, I understand \Nbut he tried...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run as wild as you want \Non the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my son from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown's luck \Nas a pirate has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the way \NCaptain Buggy will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world's \Ngreatest prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got it wrong! I said \N"my" - jumping the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still the vice warden, \NHannyabal. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's just start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me put these Sea Prism \NStone handcuffs on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a prisoner but you put handcuffs \Non me. You couldn't be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Public execution of Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in 33 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Reunion in Hell?! The Man \NWho Ate the Chop-Chop Fruit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Prism Stone handcuffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of taking a risk \Nand sneaking out very quick but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can turn \Nanything to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I can't go \Nany farther with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my power while \Nwearing those Sea Prism cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll take my cloak \Naway so I can't hide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could do more but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? I wouldn't \Nhave made it this far without your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get in even though the \Nbuilding is surrounded. I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built this place as a \Nfort that locks people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they catch you, you'll \Nnever be able to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're strong
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but promise me that you \Nwon't get in any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so \Nmuch, Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget what you've \Ndone for me. I owe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call \Nme Hancock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I got you, Hammock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have more, \NHammock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you \Ndoing, Hammock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can die happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can revert \Nthem now! I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, he loves me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's being careful about doing it \Nbecause Hancock is an important figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thorough body search...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Do you think that's \Nwhat they're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you imagining?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Warden Hannyabal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not getting any visuals from the snail in \Nthat room! Is something going on in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Domino! Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the pretext of checking what's \Ngoing on in the room as a vice warden,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is a chance for me to \Nsee Hancock's body search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body search is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting visuals \Nagain! Everything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Did I take \Ntoo much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is fine here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy with \Nthis. I'm not a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But that's the \Nrule here at Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. Feels like I've \Nlost a part of my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, let's \Ntake the big elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go \Ndown to level 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Burning Heat Floor \Nwhere Warden Magellan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot there so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank You"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "I love you"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Hancock-dono! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to \Nher all of sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that the elevator was \Ngoing down to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hancock said that Ace \Nmight be held underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Vivre Card would \Nhelp at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blugoris are returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got food! \NOpen the hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good job!\N--Take the meat to the refrigeration room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake? We'll pass \Nthrough level 1 shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worse than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This floor only contains \Nprisoners with light sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 1 of Impel Down \Nis the Crimson Floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it "Crimson"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, level 2 is the Floor \Nof Wild Beasts from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 3 in the basement \Nis the Starvation Floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And level 4 that we're heading \Nto is the Burning Heat Floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna take a \Nwhile to get to level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, you'll hear the \Npleasant screams of prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is "Fire Fist" Ace in level 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he isn't. We have more levels \Nthan that and "Fire Fist" Ace is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace should be \Ndown these stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell us that you \Nhad that kind of ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being tortured every day and night \Nhere is like dying a thousand deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna just \Nrun out on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I don't remember \Nmaking friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like a free, wild eagle! If you don't \Nlike it, why don't you do what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can't! Then you \Nhave to die like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kiss my ass!\N--I'll get you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already forgot about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Surveillance \NTransponder Snail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown who escaped \Nfrom community cell #4 of level 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in the hallway in \Nfront of solitary cell #22!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance Transponder \NSnail #71 has been shut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear \Nthat? It's Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you try to \Nescape alone! That serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna get the \Nworst punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Blugoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Vivre Card keeps \Nleading me down but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's prisoner #8200!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hiding the fact that he ate Devil \NFruit! Don't forget a Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split into two and get \Nhim from both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:54.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,700)}"Level 1: Crimson Floor"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scream? Forget it \N- I gotta get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away! Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"DANGER"? It's not like \Nanyone is gonna touch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see that coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The traps over \Nhere have gone off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Somebody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like they \Naren't coming. Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! How \Ndid you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out? I got \Nin from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Quit lying, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? You don't look \Nlike a jailer or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you behind bars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you guys are irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Do you \Nknow where Ace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ace that you're \Ntalking about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist" Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm here to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard that \Nhe just got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have put him on level \N5. You can't get anywhere near it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That floor holds all the criminals with \Nbounties of hundreds of millions or more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you run to the jailers' \Nroom and bring us some keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Please, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be fate that brought \Nus together in this big world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Blugori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blugori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, young man! \NThey're gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! What're those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! Don't mess with \Na Chop-Chop Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Shut up! You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as annoying as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that \Nthey also got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here on my own \Nwill! No one got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody comes to a \Nprison on his own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? Don't tell me that you \Nheard that I was captured
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you came \Nhere to rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Stupid! \NThat's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Hancock that I \Nwouldn't get into any trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you got me involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm \Nenjoying this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:22:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy's Peaceful Escape \NPlan is officially ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ahead of us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Should we just fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you \Nthinking, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how painful \Nall the torture's been!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cold-blooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doesn't matter if we don't get caught!\N--What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry! My cover's \Nalready been blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I don't like \Nabout you and Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys always stay \Npositive in a bad sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy joins up with Buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they use Buggy's Chop-Chop \NFruit power to get through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the prison and find Ace's floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But level 1 of the prison, the Crimson Hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shows its terrifying true \Nform and impedes their path.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break through the Crimson Hell!\NBuggy's Chaos-Inducing Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
